Source: gnome-activities
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: GNOME Activities Team <gnome-activities@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), python3, python3-pip, python3-setuptools
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: gnome-activities
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-dbus, wmctrl, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: gnome-shell
Description: KDE-like activities manager for GNOME
 GNOME Activities brings KDE Activities-like task management to GNOME.
 It manages named workspaces/contexts, remembers which apps and files
 are open per activity, and restores them when switching.
